Macro Definition Documentation

◆ pj_log_wrapper_1

#define pj_log_wrapper_1 (   arg)    pj_log_1 arg

Internal function to write log with verbosity 1. Will evaluate to empty expression if PJ_LOG_MAX_LEVEL is below 1.

Parameters
argLog expression.
